            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Line a baking tray (or two!) with <strong>non-stick baking paper</strong></p><p>Roll the <strong>pastry </strong>tightly over the filling and continue to roll until you have a log-shape, seal-side down</p><p>Make cuts into the log[s] widthways so there are 4 sections per person (making sure not to cut all the way through) – this is your <strong>cut sausage roll</strong></p><p>Transfer the <strong>cut sausage roll[s]</strong> to the baking tray[s]</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1667303676323-x200.jpg",
