    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Combine the <strong>remaining red wine vinegar</strong> and <strong>remaining cranberry sauce </strong>to a small bowl with a small drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>cranberry dressing</strong></p>",
