    {
      "instruction": "<p>To serve, spoon the <strong>apple chutney </strong>into the centre of the <strong>pork & leek sausage roll wreath</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>chicken salt chips</strong> and <strong>salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle the salad with the <strong>cranberry dressing</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
